Package helio.materialiser.executors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractExecutableMapping
    This class implements the methods required to generate RDF either following a synchronous or an asynchronous approach
    AbstractTimerExecutableMapping  
    AsynchronousExecutableMapping
    This class wraps SynchronousExecutableMapping in order for them to be executed asynchronously.
    ExecutableLinkRule
    This objects wraps a LinkRule extending its functionalities, enabling deciding whether two subjects should be linked, producing such link, and storing the link in the MaterialiserCache
    ExecutableRecursiveRule
    An alternative implementation of the ExecutableRule.
    ExecutableRule
    This objects wraps a Rule extending its functionalities, instantiating the Rule with data from the DataSource, generating a set of RDF triples, and storing the generated data in the MaterialiserCache
    SynchronousExecutableMapping
    This class implements a synchronous task that generates RDF
